searchableProductInfo.editorsNotes: Yves Saint Laurent's 'Cabas Chyc' tote combines leopard-print calf hair and leather for a luxurious slant on safari-inspired chic. The rich medley of chocolate, cream and gray gives this spacious carryall new-season appeal. Showcase this trophy bag with a color-blocked sweater and lacquered leggings for a sophisticated downtown look.Shown here with: Narciso Rodriguez top, Eddie Borgo bracelet and ring, Pamela Love ring, The Row pants, Jimmy Choo shoes.
